{"tid":174412,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得依加mh好垃圾","createTime":"2017-03-26T18:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T09:19:17.000Z","uid":72257,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef78f4e8aea16c18f37b121e8a64b5d65ef50a2e","tid":174412,"uid":72257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:39:03.000Z","msg":"我由mh2玩到mhx <br />\n中學晚晚係m記連機打龍,儲野升裝,仲記得比金獅子滅團<br />\n開頭mh3都覺得唔錯,更新左水戰,又可以上網打<br />\n去到mh4,mhx跟本年年都一9樣<br />\n開頭都忍話遊戲性高唔洗畫質<br />\n希望下集又會改善or出係其他機(switch都好）<br />\n但比左6年時間,2017仲要睇有碼<br />\n加少少龍改少少打法又一年<br />\nD龍仲要越黎越廢<br />\n曬左咁多時間係隻垃圾game到<br />\n<br />\n利申 mh死忠"},{"pid":"9c294d8e7e1653626f0cac87ab49750d33b9393e","tid":174412,"uid":17352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:51:52.000Z","msg":"隻xx拎黎賺最後一水姐<br />\n3ds你想系統會點大變法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會係你有太多幻想搞到自己失望"},{"pid":"93ee855c717512ac2ab7d57c228a438518fcf2c1","tid":174412,"uid":5914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:58:18.000Z","msg":"啱呀"},{"pid":"3c002e5d0e56a3b1dfe6e59237dbb19d7c8dc4a8","tid":174412,"uid":2592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T21:23:51.000Z","msg":"Xx同2啲畫面比好似冇分別咁<br />\n雖然我唔係j開畫面，但差唔多10年都冇進步真係幾難接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前一貪跑即買，宜家真係不了"},{"pid":"817926cccc91adddb893d553b65e15afa9e4a228","tid":174412,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T22:05:56.000Z","msg":"唔好講咁多，樓主索狗"},{"pid":"99072607446379c09ee70e606cd3b0e0ec8a8733","tid":174412,"uid":36169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T04:42:18.000Z","msg":"如果當初 mh 繼續係 ps4 有得玩，畫質同地圖有幾正，有無可以gta級數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54964ad5daacfcbe0cbb7812268af1a919a5